{"tid":1491932,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"如果依一世只能夠睇一套電影, 你會睇邊套 ?","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:55:47.000Z","uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"80d24cc5a6515b95b95e9176e136d866effef1cd","tid":1491932,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"講下原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514363b571ea6359da7317844b98658ff46db7f6","tid":1491932,"uid":2562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"364d047b5608fcc1d889dbdf10e40bf2d6d0295a","tid":1491932,"uid":54346,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FsTPphm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsTPphm.jpg&h=f624b7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n822 集會 823人鏈 824 觀塘 825 荃灣"},{"pid":"6e391df1cc05bd95fc2a197b7c6ffce7087f2153","tid":1491932,"uid":240648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"國產凌凌漆"},{"pid":"9f594b54a59d3b0aec05c8fc034e42b23338f5f5","tid":1491932,"uid":232575,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:31:48.000Z","msg":"(Batman) The Dark Knight Returns (2012-2013)動畫上下集<br />\n<br />\n命題思考「正義與制度」之間o既「既對立又共生」o既關係。<br />\n鍾意佢畫風畫大夠「大舊衰」。未睇之前唔明點解要畫到BATMAN咁肥咁唔青靚白靜。個造形同畫風令我一直唔想睇，睇完先知點解要畫到咁肥。令我知道以前諗野幾細路，一個角色有幾正義唔係睇外形有幾中二病。依部原著漫畫幾乎影響之後所有蝙蝠俠作品，定立老蝙蝠俠形像。內容對我來講比The Dark Knight 2008更有深度。<br />\n<br />\n以下係劇透讀書報告!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高潮位1<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">變種人集團睇到蝙蝠俠打敗自己大佬，決定改名做蝙蝠俠之子，學蝙蝠俠行俠杖義，而蝙蝠俠就帶領佢地試一次伸張正義。原來人犯罪既目的可能只係搵唔到自我價值。</span><br />\n高潮位2<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">蝙蝠俠打超人。正義=/=政府，就算政府有超人都好，只要政府行邪道，蝙蝠俠血肉之驅都會行出來打超人。</span><br />\n結局<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">蝙蝠俠決定訓練蝙蝠俠之子做接班人。話我知正義唔係個人英雄主義，而係令罪人贖罪同搵返自己正面既自我價值。做英雄追求既「唔係社會崇拜自己，而係社會唔再需要自己」    </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">蝙蝠俠為既唔係榮譽(虛榮)，而係the better world</span>"},{"pid":"87764b64d09f79d0561c8007331b9fa1a78c7f69","tid":1491932,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:32:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"042a0c75ee2cd0f3b3415524d59207aa89733970","tid":1491932,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"熱血高校"},{"pid":"202619eb518e14fa1de5f332a4107ef600082dae","tid":1491932,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:37:46.000Z","msg":"Fight club"},{"pid":"63e0630db9e6d853c4e63bb338a0a92689316540","tid":1491932,"uid":62755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:38:35.000Z","msg":"about time<br />\n獲益良多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719273e06588f0defb2b3aec6993987727c7d664","tid":1491932,"uid":115601,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"十年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7aVkA0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt